name: shantaeAI (Style embedding)
description:
This is a style embedding inspired by the artwork of the Shantae games. It's nothing major, but if you like the sometimes very amusing / funny style: this is for you!

Also check out my other embeddings here.

Trained on waifu-diffusion-v1-3-float32.ckpt, but works best when used in connection with DreamShaper 3.3 or Anything 3.0.

I used Anything-V3.0 VAE or vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned. Both work fine.

The keyword is the filename (without the .pt) you put into your embeddings folder (usually shantae_styleAI).

modelVersions.description:
Initial release.

Dataset images: 13
Model used: waifu-diffusion-v1-3-float32.ckpt
Number of vectors: 4
Batch size: 13
Gradient steps: 1
Learning rate: 0.005:800, 0.002:1300, 0.0005
Steps: 1100
Latent sampling method: once
